<h1>Vonage Verify API Demo</h1>
<img src="/img/Voyagers_Meet-the-Voyagers.png" alt="Vonage Voyagers: Meet the Voyagers">

<p>This is a demo showing an basic implementation of a two-factor authentication user log-in flow using the <a href="https://developer.vonage.com/en/verify/overview" target="_blank">Vonage Verfy API</a> in a Ruby on Rails application.</p>
<p>The 2FA implementation is built on top of the code and business logic created by the Rails `authentication` generator.</p>

<h2>Homepage</h2>
<p>The Homepage can be accessed by any user, authenticated or unauthenticated.</p>
